data.description: This is a gorgeous 3 bedroom and 2 bath home sit on little over 1 acres of land. This home has plenty of storage, and separate utility room. Master bedroom has (his) and (hers) walk in closet with a full bathroom. The kitchen is huge with granite counter tops. Floor plan lead to open living room and kitchen area with beautiful french door that covered patio and lead out to on ground pool. The property has fruit trees and it has a small pond with gold fish in there. Has a shed on the property that can be turn into another living space. The property is very private and perfect place to spend time with your family.
